    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h2><p>教会别人是最好的学习方式，俗话说“好记性不如烂笔头”，做笔记可以提升自己的写作、总结能力，所以养成写博客的好习惯对自己是很有意的。写博客除了可以用市面上CSDN、博客园、简书、掘金等平台，也可以搭建一套自己的博客，本文着重讲一下使用hexo搭建博客。</p><p>目前较多人采用的博客搭建方案各有优缺点，有如下几种：</p><ul><li>Git+Github+Markdown+jekyll （免费）</li><li>Git+Github+Markdown+hexo （免费）</li><li>虚拟主机＋插件＋Wordpress （付费）</li></ul><h2 id="搭建环境"><a href="#搭建环境" class="headerlink" title="搭建环境"></a>搭建环境</h2><h3 id="安装Node"><a href="#安装Node" class="headerlink" title="安装Node"></a>安装Node</h3><p>Node.js用来生成静态页面</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">Node.js</a>下载相应平台的最新版本，然后安装即可</p></li><li><p>使用<code>Homebrew</code>安装</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">安装</span></span><br><span class="line">brew install node</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看版本</span></span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="安装Git"><a href="#安装Git" class="headerlink" title="安装Git"></a>安装Git</h3><p>把本地的hexo内容提交到github上去. 安装Xcode就自带有Git</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">Git</a>下载最新版本，然后安装即可</p></li><li><p>使用<code>Homebrew</code>安装</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">安装</span></span><br><span class="line">brew install git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看版本</span></span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="安装HEXO"><a href="#安装HEXO" class="headerlink" title="安装HEXO"></a>安装HEXO</h3><p>Node和Git都安装好后，可执行如下命令安装<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">Hexo</a>：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">安装</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo npm install -g hexo</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看版本</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="hexo创建本地博客"><a href="#hexo创建本地博客" class="headerlink" title="hexo创建本地博客"></a>hexo创建本地博客</h2><h3 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h3><p>创建一个文件夹，如：Blog，cd到Blog里执行一下命令。然后它会自动在Blog文件夹下生成一些配置文件，这个Blog文件夹就是博客的根目录。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">创建本地博客</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地预览"><a href="#本地预览" class="headerlink" title="本地预览"></a>本地预览</h3><ul><li><p>通过以下命令启动本地服务，进行预览调试</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">清除缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">hexo generate生成静态页面，会在当前目录下生成一个新的叫做public的文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">hexo server启动本地服务，进行文章预览调试</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>浏览器输入<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a>查看效果</p></li><li><p>常见错误：</p><ul><li><p>报错：<code>ERROR Plugin load failed: hexo-server</code></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo npm install hexo-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>报错：</code>Usage: hexo<Command> ….  `          </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-server --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>[http://localhost:4000](http://localhost:4000)打不开或者内容为空</code> </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-ejs --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-marked --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="更改主题"><a href="#更改主题" class="headerlink" title="更改主题"></a>更改主题</h3><ul><li><p>刚创建的博客默认使用的主题是<code>landscape</code>，去<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">主题集合</a>中挑选自己喜欢的样式，我使用的是 <a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next">hexo-theme-next</a></p></li><li><p>手动前往 <a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next">hexo-theme-next</a>下载，下载完成之后放到<code>Blog/themes</code>目录下；</p><p>或在<code>Bolg</code>目录文件下终端输入一下命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="built_in">cd</span>到Blog里执行命令</span></span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code>下<code>_config.yml</code>文件，修改<code>theme: landscape为theme: next</code>，前提是你已经下载完了next主题，然后本地预览查看效果  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105131451.png" style="zoom:43%;" /></p></li></ul><h3 id="主题设定"><a href="#主题设定" class="headerlink" title="主题设定"></a>主题设定</h3><ul><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code>下站点配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，修改名称、描述、作者、语言等主要配置项；  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105133820.png" style="zoom:43%;" /></p></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg/themes/next</code>下主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，修改 Scheme、菜单、侧边栏、头像等配置项；可参考[NEXT主题官方  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105135353.png" style="zoom:60%;" /></p></li></ul><h2 id="部署到GitHub"><a href="#部署到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="部署到GitHub"></a>部署到GitHub</h2><h3 id="创建项目"><a href="#创建项目" class="headerlink" title="创建项目"></a>创建项目</h3><ul><li>登录Github创建一个新项目，项目名必须为： `用户名.github.io  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105140929.png"/></li></ul><h3 id="修改配置文件"><a href="#修改配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改配置文件"></a>修改配置文件</h3><ul><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code>下站点配置文件<code>_config.yml</code></p></li><li><p>hexo在2点几的版本中type: github。之后的版本是type: git  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105142701.png" style="zoom:43%;" /></p></li></ul><h3 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h3><ul><li><p>执行如下命令安装插件后才能使用git部署</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>每次部署的步骤，都可按以下三步来进行。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">清除缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">重新生成静态文件，hexo generate</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">部署发布到Github，hexo deploy</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="博客发布"><a href="#博客发布" class="headerlink" title="博客发布"></a>博客发布</h2><ul><li><p>进入<code>Bolg</code>目录下，执行以下命令</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">新建文章</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new post &quot;文章名称&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>这时Bolg\source\ _posts下可以看到刚新建的”文章名称.md”文件</p></li><li><p>打开文件，使用Markdown语法编辑博客。</p></li><li><p>编辑完成后，先本地预览然后部署到github上</p></li></ul><h2 id="接入其他实用功能"><a href="#接入其他实用功能" class="headerlink" title="接入其他实用功能"></a>接入其他实用功能</h2><h3 id="添加-RSS-输出功能"><a href="#添加-RSS-输出功能" class="headerlink" title="添加 RSS 输出功能"></a>添加 RSS 输出功能<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105155820.png" style="zoom:5%;" /></h3><p>对于 <code>RSS</code> 输出功能，<code>Hexo</code> 已经有一个现成的插件可以用，那就是 <a href="https://link.jianshu.com/?t=https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-generator-feed">hexo-generator-feed</a> ，下面就来分享一下使用方法。</p><ul><li><p>首先打开终端 <code>cd</code> 到本地的 <code>Bolg</code> 目录下，输入以下命令安装 <code>RSS</code> 插件。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code> 根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，加入以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">feed:</span><br><span class="line">type: atom</span><br><span class="line">path: atom.xml</span><br><span class="line">limit: 20</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg/themes/next</code>下主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，设置 <code>RSS</code> 地址：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rss: /atom.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>最后打开终端 <code>cd</code> 到本地的 <code>Bolg</code> 目录下，输入以下命令重新部署一下博客 。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="Gitment评论系统"><a href="#Gitment评论系统" class="headerlink" title="Gitment评论系统"></a>Gitment评论系统</h3><p>我选择接入<a href="https://github.com/imsun/gitment">Gitment</a>，当然你也可以官方文档 <a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/third-party-services.html">http://theme-next.iissnan.com/third-party-services.html</a> 接入其它三方评论系统。</p><ul><li><p>注册Github OAuth Application</p><p>登录Github<code>-&gt;</code>点击头像<code>-&gt;</code>Settings<code>-&gt;</code>Developer settings<code>-&gt;</code>Oauth Apps<code>-&gt;</code>New OAuth App`</p><p><strong>Application name</strong>:随便写</p><p><strong>Homepage URL</strong>:这个也可以随意写,就写你的博客地址就行</p><p><strong>Application description</strong>:描述,也可以随意写</p><p><strong>Authorization callback URL</strong>:这个必须写你的博客地址</p></li></ul><p><code>得到client_id、client_secret信息，下面要用到。</code></p>  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105172404.png" style="zoom:33%;" /><p>  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105173458.png"></p><ul><li><p>安装Gitment</p><ul><li><p>首先打开终端 <code>cd</code> 到本地的 <code>Bolg</code> 目录下，输入以下命令安装。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save gitment</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul><p>修改主题配置</p><p>  <code>themes/next/_config.yml</code>:</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Introduction: https://imsun.net/posts/gitment-introduction/</span></span><br><span class="line">gitment:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  mint: true # RECOMMEND, A mint on Gitment, to support count, language and proxy_gateway</span><br><span class="line">  count: true # Show comments count in post meta area</span><br><span class="line">  lazy: false # Comments lazy loading with a button</span><br><span class="line">  cleanly: false # Hide &#x27;Powered by ...&#x27; on footer, and more</span><br><span class="line">  language: # Force language, or auto switch by theme</span><br><span class="line">  github_user: &#123;you github user id&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  github_repo: 新建一个存储评论的仓库，这里填写仓库名</span><br><span class="line">  client_id: &#123;刚才申请的ClientID&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  client_secret: &#123;刚才申请的Client Secret&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  proxy_gateway: # Address of api proxy, See: https://github.com/aimingoo/intersect</span><br><span class="line">  redirect_protocol: # Protocol of redirect_uri with force_redirect_protocol when mint enabled</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>issue的Label有长度限制,对于中文博客来说,中文标题很容易就超过长度限制,所以需要做一下特殊处理,修改<code>themes/next/layout/_third-party/comments/gitment.swig</code>:</p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var gitment = new &#123;&#123;CommentsClass&#125;&#125;(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     id: &#x27;&#123;&#123; page.date &#125;&#125;&#x27;,</span><br><span class="line">     owner: &#x27;&#123;&#123; theme.gitment.github_user &#125;&#125;&#x27;,</span><br><span class="line">     repo: &#x27;&#123;&#123; theme.gitment.github_repo &#125;&#125;&#x27;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>object ProgressEvent</p><p>  出现这个问题是由于作者在<code>gitment.browser.js</code>中硬编码了自己的服务器人证域名:<code>https://gh-oauth.imsun.net</code>，现在域名过期了,要么自己搭一个认证服务器，要么可以用其他人的，在gitment的issues里面找到了答案:<a href="https://github.com/imsun/gitment/issues/175">#175</a>,需要把Hexo你所用的主题中的引用文件给改一下，我用的是next主题,改动方法如下:</p><p>  修改<code>themes/next/layout/_third-party/comments/gitment.swig</code></p>  <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- LOCAL: You can save these files to your site and update links --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% if theme.gitment.mint %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;% set CommentsClass = &quot;Gitmint&quot; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://aimingoo.github.io/gitmint/style/default.css&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;script src=&quot;https://aimingoo.github.io/gitmint/dist/gitmint.browser.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% else %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;% set CommentsClass = &quot;Gitment&quot; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://imsun.github.io/gitment/style/default.css&quot;&gt; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- &lt;script src=&quot;https://imsun.github.io/gitment/dist/gitment.browser.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-gitment@1/default.css&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-gitment@1/gitment.browser.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- END LOCAL --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  注释的部分是原来的地址，后面的是引用的网友的解决方案地址,需要注意的是确保<code>themes/next/_config.yml</code>中<code>theme.gitment.mint</code>设置为false,才会走到我们改动的分支.</p><p>初始化评论插件</p><h3 id="访问量"><a href="#访问量" class="headerlink" title="访问量"></a>访问量</h3><p><a href="http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/">不蒜子访问量统计</a></p><h3 id="字数统计、阅读速度"><a href="#字数统计、阅读速度" class="headerlink" title="字数统计、阅读速度"></a>字数统计、阅读速度</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/willin/hexo-wordcount">hexo-wordcount</a></p><h3 id="本地搜索"><a href="#本地搜索" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索"></a>本地搜索</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-generator-searchdb">hexo-generator-searchdb</a></p><h3 id="Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌"><a href="#Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌" class="headerlink" title="Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌"></a>Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌</h3><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/8c0707ce5da4">Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
